<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{full_lang} {project} Top 100 on {formatted_date}</title>
    <script src="../../../../js/jquery.js"></script>
    <link href='../../../../css/fonts.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <link href='../../../../css/chart.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <style>
    {#articles}
    .cover-{rank} {
        background: url({image_url});
        background-size: cover; 
        background-position: 50%; 
    }
    {/articles}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>{full_lang} {project} <span class="ultra">Top 100</span></h1>
            <p>The most-visited {full_lang} {project} articles, updated daily. <a href="#about" class="learn">Learn more</a>...</p> 
            <div class="subtitle light">{?prev}<a class="issue_nav left" href="../../../../{prev}">&larr;</a>{:else}<span class="left issue_nav"></span>{/prev}<p class="center">{formatted_date}</p>{?next}<a class="issue_nav right" href="../../../../{next}">&rarr;</a>{:else}<span class="right issue_nav"></span>{/next}
            <br style="clear: left;" />
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <ul>
            {#articles}
            <li class="row">
                <div class="column rank"><p><a href="#rank-{rank}">{rank}</a></p></div>
                <a class="column cover-art cover-{rank}" href="{url}" target="_blank"></a>
                <div class="column label">
                    <a id="rank-{rank}"></a>
                    <a id="title-{article}"></a>
                    <p class="title"><a href="{url}" target="_blank">{title}</a></p>
                    <p class="summary">{summary}</p>
                    <div class="meta-area">
                        <p class="views">{views} views <span class="meta">({view_trend|s}{view_delta} from yesterday)</span></p>
                        <p class="streak">{@gt key=streak value=1}{streak} day streak{/gt}</p>
                        <a href="http://twitter.com/share?text={tweet}&amp;url={permalink}" target="_blank"><img class="twitter-icon" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/9f/Twitter_bird_logo_2012.svg/18px-Twitter_bird_logo_2012.svg.png"></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            {/articles}
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-area">
        <div class="container footer">
            <h2>About</h2>
            <p>Learn more on the <a href="#">Hatnote Blog</a>.</p>
            <p><a name="about"></a>A daily list of the most visited {project} articles, generated by <a href="https://twitter.com/sklaporte">Stephen LaPorte</a> and <a href="https://twitter.com/mhashemi">Mahmoud Hashemi</a>. Wikipedia articles are written by thousands of people and read by billions more. If you find this list interesting, you will enjoy <a href="http://weekly.hatnote.com">The Weeklypedia</a>, a weekly digest of the most edited Wikipedia articles.</p>
            <p>This page was made possible by <a href="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/?doc#!/Pageviews_data/get_metrics_pageviews_top_project_access_year_month_day">{project}'s new page view API</a>, with some nice images and summaries from the <a href="https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/API:Query">MediaWiki API</a>. You can find more code and documentation <a href="https://github.com/hatnote/top">available on github</a>.</p>
            <p>Want to see a list of the most visited articles in another language of Wikipedia? So do we! Please <a href="https://github.com/hatnote/top/issues">send a request</a> and let us know if you can help translate the templates.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
    (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){
    (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),
    m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)
    })(window,document,'script','//www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga');
    ga('create', 'UA-40320359-1', 'hatnote.com');
    ga('send', 'pageview');
    </script>
</body>
</html>
